item.title: Tenpin Bowling climb BUCS Rankings
item.author: Tsz Ki Chiu,
item.description: BUCS Tenpin Bowling Championship took place in Sheffield last weekend. The results were resounding. Former Captain Michael Lau and Former Vice-Captain Hui Erh Tay, our favourite bowlers, achieved 605 and 601 three-game series.
